  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">We've been invited to give a number of seminars and speaking events.</p>

  <p class="mb-10 leading-relaxed">These are great opportunities to pass on knowledge developed through our research and practical experience, as well as opportunity to connect with new generations of students, academia and the wider industry.</p>

  <h2 class="mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">The University of Sussex</h2>
  <p class="mb-14 leading-relaxed">Our Director was invited to give a talk to the Dynamics, Control and Vehicle research group at the University of Sussex in April 2021.</p>

  <h2 class="mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">MIA School of Race Engineering</h2>
  <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">In October 2020, Wavey Dynamics was asked by the MIA to give a seminar on motorsport suspension technology at their School of Race Engineering.</p>

